environments

☀️ Databricks SQL now supports Temporary Tables. Temp Tables are session-scoped, so you can build and test SQL logic without creating permanent tables. Automatic cleanup at the end of each session keeps your Unity Catalog clean and tidy. It's a beautiful day.

Do you build SQL-based ETL pipelines? Learn more about how easy it is to get started with Temp Tables in the blog: https://lnkd.in/g2XB4Tng